{"tid":190630,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[背囊]有冇人有用JOEY Backpack 或者 Invisible backpack??","createTime":"2017-04-07T08:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:06:55.000Z","uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37e1435398fd4c57e14451b9def618b223207465","tid":190630,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:53:06.000Z","msg":"想睇下用家有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nInvisible backpack 好似好深，拎野會唔會唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJOEY Backpack 我見佢背位係彎，會唔會放得好少野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我見佢都有25L<br />\n<br />\n或者有冇其他靚靚仔仔既推介？"},{"pid":"b2186110d9a80ccd2d3c483ea5b7801c9e8d9468","tid":190630,"uid":11293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"同問，最近都想買Invisible"},{"pid":"4d1bdf202ae0552981a4e40965901c9c4f0dff1c","tid":190630,"uid":5954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"買左joey,，佢main aera唔係好大，同埋好多一格格袋，如果你喜歡多格袋，應該唔錯"},{"pid":"7047b24c85cc6d403a767a7402cbc28a776a3d88","tid":190630,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左joey,，佢main aera唔係好大，同埋好多一格格袋，如果你喜歡多格袋，應該唔錯</blockquote><br />\n會唔會放得好少野？<br />\n見佢彎彎地，好似會無左啲位咁"},{"pid":"3f2a19dab4173baa1db2815a1ca9e69df4a0becc","tid":190630,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左joey,，佢main aera唔係好大，同埋好多一格格袋，如果你喜歡多格袋，應該唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以post咩住個袋既背面圖比我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我youtube睇介紹片d人死都唔show成個咩住袋既背面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇產品介紹圖又好重味精味，明明睇youtube個背普通，張圖上背圖又靚左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想睇下現實係點。<br />\n<br />\n另外想問巴打覺得個袋咩上身靚唔靚，會唔會太闊?"},{"pid":"3b2f04da1b8d1659b7a4bb80c002a9b229809f6f","tid":190630,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買左joey,，佢main aera唔係好大，同埋好多一格格袋，如果你喜歡多格袋，應該唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以post咩住個袋既背面圖比我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我youtube睇介紹片d人死都唔show成個咩住袋既背面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇產品介紹圖又好重味精味，明明睇youtube個<span style=\"color: red;\">袋</span>普通，張圖上背圖又靚左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想睇下現實係點。<br />\n<br />\n另外想問巴打覺得個袋咩上身靚唔靚，會唔會太闊?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"115e1bffe33fb8c19a7bdd9c34df6e802e4446f5","tid":190630,"uid":15232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"我買左Invisible backpack同Joey2款, Invisible個隻Main area幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,如果For旅行買手信真係幾好用,可以放到2盒手野都OK(如果唔係太大盒個啲),但個袋勁易塌左落黎,一唔夠野裝就會勁DER皮同埋個太重個底都會DER哂成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,重有就係個背隻係絨毛黎,香港夏天揹勁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,而JOEY個隻MAIN AREA真係唔算大,但佢有得加大,所以都OK,但我覺得勁好揹,D重量唔會話聚哂落個底到,不過個袋本身個背板係重D同硬身,所以相對地個袋本身都有啲重咁,因為個背太硬,所以裝野黎講唔算好有彈性,巴打可以諗諗,而加我主要用JOEY因為個揹帶舒服D同成舍背囊貼身D,相對黎講比較舒服,如果要揹多野就Invisible backpack,長時間揹就JOEY會好D"},{"pid":"a4c55c58d0d7f14a39d6fc2abd00fe73e84ae8b0","tid":190630,"uid":10371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"本身都想買joey，跟住今朝落街見到人揹到隻袋好似好闊好肥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a439d7fd976d674a41dc7426d61c6b106470001","tid":190630,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"講咁耐都未有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5c2ad83209bc26de19bdbe2a42fc00c5141099","tid":190630,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1377290f7072f1705fdcbef123c6653d58a21a","tid":190630,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a67578f89bd108c5fb1dcb690be24563d01523","tid":190630,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://searchingc.com/collections/joey-backpack/?gclid=CPfvjO7FrdMCFQl8vQodcgsKHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fcollections%2Fjoey-backpack%2F%3Fgclid%3DCPfvjO7FrdMCFQl8vQodcgsKHw&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0ad77588\" target=\"_blank\">http://searchingc.com/collections/joey-backpack/?gclid=CPfvjO7FrdMCFQl8vQodcgsKHw</a><br />\n問點解佢可以賣得平過官網，佢話同官方有合作，信唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsend左email去官網問，佢地未覆。"}]}